	----------------------------------------

	    CONNEX is Connect-4 with a twist
	  you can optionally play to lose!
	  Try to get/avoid 4 in a line in any
	  direction by dropping your pieces
	  in the columns. Use the MOUSE to
	  select columns, or type the number
	  (1 - 7). Also ESC aborts play. Hit
	  F1 NOW for no of players, or F2
	  for win/lose mode. Do try play-to-
	  lose, its a real challenge! For a 
	  demo, select 0 players for auto-
	  play. Full instructions are within
	  the game.

